Package: libarmadito-pdf-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: i386 amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libarmadito-pdf (>= 0.12.0), pkg-config
Description: Armadito PDF library - development files
 Provides support for Armadito PDF functionnalities (Parsing, Analysis)
 The package contains the needed headers and libraries for developing software using the libarmadito-pdf interface.